Julie Duncan https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Julie_Duncan 0 Julie Duncan (born 17 January 1919 in Cornish, New Hampshire; died 20 June 1986) was a motion picture actress specialising in short subjects and Westerns. She was a champion steeplechase rider. Julie_Duncan ( born 17_January_1919 in Cornish , New_Hampshire ; died 20_June_1986 ) was a_motion_picture_actress specialising in short_subjects_and_Westerns . She was a_champion_steeplechase_rider .
